Instruction for Download & play

# Solar-System-Simulation Vr. 0.1 Demo

Latest Releases: https://github.com/ImAbuSayed/Solar-System-Simulation/releases

To Play:-

Step1:
Download Setup File (Solar Simulation Setup (x64).exe).

Step2:
Setup
and 
Play

Simulation Instruction:
You can see a different view by click on a different planet.iew by click on planet.
and
Close game Alt+Ctrl+F4.

Check My Latest Articles and Projects.
